       fhir:comment [ fhir:v "The subject of an action overrides the subject at a parent action or on the root of the PlanDefinition if specified.\n\nIn addition, because the subject needs to be resolved during realization, use of subjects in actions (or in the ActivityDefinition referenced by the action) resolves based on the set of subjects supplied in context and by type (i.e. the patient subject would resolve to a resource of type Patient)." ] ;
